translated: Claesson, Bertil, dentist, Gis^la-ved, b. October 25th, 1912 in Stockholm. Finished high school in Örebro in 1933, graduated with a dentistry degree in 1936, and became a licensed dentist in 1940. Practiced dentistry in Gis-laved with a secondary practice in Anders torp from 1941 to 1946.
